                            <comment id="13477561" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 17 Oct 2012 03:11:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FIS.close says &quot;If this stream has an associated channel then the channel is closed as well.&quot;  So closing both source and channel is unnecessary.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13477577" author="xedin" created="Wed, 17 Oct 2012 03:38:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Right, sorry, they share the same fd. Re-attached the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13477927" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 17 Oct 2012 14:52:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
